pam-ssh-auth-info (1.6.20220918) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Changed license to GPL/LGPL-3+.
  * Changed pam_sm_setcred to succeed or fail based on SSH
    authentication information (instead of merely returning PAM_IGNORE
    unconditionally).
  * Fixed crash on empty extended patterns.
  * Preferred all_of/any_of options over all/any options.
  * Added support for the none_of option.
  * Improved documentation.

 -- Eero Häkkinen <Eero+pam-ssh-auth-info@xn--Hkkinen-5wa.fi>  Sun, 18 Sep 2022 20:03:04 +0300

